$ tag object [git]

A *tag object* points to a → development/version-control-systems/git/objects/commit or another tag object.

It can contain a message, just like a commit object.

{ Signed tag object

  If the tag object contains a PGP signature, it is called a «signed tag object».

}


sa:
  development/version-control-systems/git/objects

  → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/refs/tags
  
  `→ development/version-control-systems/git/commands/tag`,
  `→ development/version-control-systems/git/commands/mktag`,
  `→ development/version-control-systems/git/commands/verify-tag`
